  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2018-09-28T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Protecting and Securing Chemical Facilities from Terrorist Attacks Act of 2018\n\nThis bill: (1) reauthorizes the Department of Homeland Security's Chemical Facility Anti-Terrorism Standards (CFATS) Program, and (2) establishes a CFATS Recognition Program with the goal of leveraging CFATS regulations and industry stewardship programs to further enhance security relating to hazardous chemicals."
  }, 
